(6, '<p>\r\n	<a class="name-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/carlos-santana-mn0000175196" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Carlos Santana</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;was originally in his own wing of the Latin Rock Hall of Fame, neither playing Afro-Cuban with rock guitar, as did&nbsp;</span><a class="name-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/malo-mn0000566113" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Malo</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, nor flavoring mainstream rock with percussion, as did&nbsp;</span><a class="name-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/chicago-mn0000110161" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Chicago</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">. His first record, as with the best fusion, created something a little different than just a mixture -- a new style that, surprisingly, remains all his own. Granted that Latin music has seeped into the mainstream since, but why aren&#39;t&nbsp;</span><a class="name-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/van-halen-mn0000260206" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Van Halen</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><a class="name-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/metallica-mn0000446509" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Metallica</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;listening to this? Where they simmer,</span><a class="name-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/santana-mn0000295756" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Santana</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;boils over.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<div>\r\n		<table class="list" style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-size: 11.818181991577148px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; width: 725.4545288085938px; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 17.99715805053711px;">\r\n			<thead>\r\n				<tr style="background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);">\r\n					<th class="sample" style="background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: 27px; height: 27px; padding: 2px 0px 3px; text-align: center; background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat repeat;">\r\n						Sample</th>\r\n					<th class="tracknum" style="background-image: none; background-attachment: s