ass="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/stomu-yamashta-mn0000622185" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Stomu Yamashta</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">), and singer&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/greg-walker-mn0000801094" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Greg Walker</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">.</span></p>\r\n<div class="paragraph" style="margin-bottom: 1em; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="thumbnail xl album inline-still right" style="margin-bottom: 3px; display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 2px 2px 2px 0px; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 2px 2px 2px 0px; background-image: url(http://www.allmusic.com/assets/images/sprite-no-image.png); float: right; margin-left: 10px; width: 210px; height: 210px; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px; background-position: -515px 5px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n	<div class="cropped-image" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden; width: 200px; height: 200px;">\r\n		<a href="http://www.allmusic.com/album/amigos-mw0000195601" oldtitle="Santana - Amigos" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial !important; outline: none; position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 200px; height: 200px; display: block; margin: 5px;"><img alt="Amigos" data-debug="250x244 (44)" height="200" src="http://cps-static.rovicorp.com/3/JPG_250/MI0002/424/MI0002424158.jpg?partner=allrovi.com" style="border: 0px; outline: none; position: absolute; left: -2px;" width="204" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">The result was&nbsp;</span><a class="album-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/album/amigos-mw0000195601" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Amigos</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, released in March 1976, which returned</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/santana-mn0000295756" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Santana</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;to the Top Ten and went gold. The band was back only nine months later with another&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/rubinson-mn0000223255" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Rubinson</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;production,&nbsp;</span><a class="album-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/album/festival-mw0000309055" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Festival</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, for which</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/santana-mn0000295756" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Santana</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;consisted of&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/carlos-mn0000175196" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Carlos</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/coster-mn0000509822" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Coster</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, returning members&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/jose-chepito-areas-mn0000268795" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Jose &quot;Chepito&quot; Areas</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/leon-patillo-mn0000198451" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Leon Patillo</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, drummer&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/gaylord-birch-mn0000768528" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Gaylord Birch</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, percussionist&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/raul-rekow-mn0000399694" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Raul Rekow</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, and bass player&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/pablo-telez-mn0001568426" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Pablo Telez</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">. This album peaked in the Top 40 and went gold. Never having issued a live album in the U.S.,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/santana-mn0000295756" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Santana</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;made up for the lapse with&nbsp;</span><a class="album-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/album/moonflower-mw0000191747" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Moonflower</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, released in October 1977; that band consisted of&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/carlos-mn0000175196" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Carlos</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/coster-mn0000509822" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Coster</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">,</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/areas-mn0000268795" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Areas</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/rekow-mn0000399694" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Rekow</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/telez-mn0001568426" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Telez</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, returning member&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/greg-walker-mn0000801094" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Greg Walker</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, percussionist</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/pete-escovedo-mn0000840760" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Pete Escovedo</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, drummer&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/graham-lear-mn0000798076" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Graham Lear</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, and bass player&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/david-margen-mn0000219687" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">David Margen</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">. The album peaked in the Top Ten and eventually went platinum, its sales stimulated by the single release of a revival of&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/the-zombies-mn0000582313" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">the Zombies</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&#39; &quot;She&#39;s Not There&quot; that peaked in the Top 20,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/santana-mn0000295756" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-fam