px;">&nbsp;staged a 20-year anniversary reunion concert in August 1986 featuring many past bandmembers. The February 1987 album</span><a class="album-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/album/freedom-mw0000191746" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Freedom</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;marked the formal inclusion of&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/buddy-miles-mn0000943936" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Buddy Miles</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">&nbsp;as a member of</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/santana-mn0000295756" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Santana</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">, alongside&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://www.allmusic.com/artist/carlos-mn0000175196" style="color: rgb(165, 3, 54); text-decoration: initial; outline: none; font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">Carlos</a><span style="font-family: Georgia, ''Palatino Linotype'', ''Book Antiqua'', serif; font-size: 15.454545021057129px; line-height: 22.5px;">,&nbsp;</span><a class="artist-link" href="http://